        </div>

        <div class="feature-item pulse-anim delay-1">
          <img src="pictures/fIREpROOF02.webp" alt="Fireproof self storage containers">
          <h3>Fire Proof</h3>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-item pulse-anim delay-2">
          <img src="pictures/MouseProof01.webp" alt="Mouse-proof storage facility Vernal Utah">
