        <li>Call James at <a href="tel:4358287710" style="color: var(--primary-dark); font-weight: 700;">435-828-7710</a> or visit us at 2225 South 3250 East, Vernal</li>
        <li>Choose your container size — 20ft ($130/mo) or 40ft ($230/mo)</li>
        <li>Sign a simple rental agreement</li>
        <li>Receive your personal access code for 24/7 entry</li>
        <li>Move in the same day</li>
      </ol>
    </div>
  </section>


